Class BehaviorTreeScript

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kraken.api.core.script.Script
      • com.kraken.api.core.script.BehaviorTreeScript
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Scriptable
    public abstract class BehaviorTreeScript
extends Script
    Base class for scripts that use a behavior tree for their logic. Users must implement the buildBehaviorTree() method to define their behavior tree structure.
